data.description: Rare find under 200k in South Habersham County. Mobile Home was put on a permanent foundation and the title retired. NEW TIN ROOF in 2022. NEW HVAC in 2017. NEW HOT WATER HEATER in 2022. 8 new windows & 3 that are older. All NEW ELECTRICAL WIRING in the home along with new electrical panel and new breakers. Home sits on 1 acre of land. Septic Tank was pumped in 2020. Large Storage Building for your lawn equipment. Above ground pool and pool equipment to remain with the home. Easy commute to Habersham and Hall Counties.
